       CLR-REG-JPT SECTION.
       INI-CLR-REG-JPT.
           MOVE SPACES TO JPT.
           PERFORM CLR-JPT-5 VARYING WSS-JPT-IFLD FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL WSS-JPT-IFLD > 5.
           PERFORM CLR-JPT-10 VARYING WSS-JPT-IFLD FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL WSS-JPT-IFLD > 10.
           PERFORM CLR-JPT-50 VARYING WSS-JPT-IFLD FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL WSS-JPT-IFLD > 50.
       FIN-CLR-REG-JPT.
           EXIT.

       CLR-JPT-5 SECTION.
       INI-CLR-JPT-5.
           MOVE ZEROES TO JPT-VAL-MNTO IN JPT(WSS-JPT-IFLD).
           MOVE ZEROES TO JPT-SGV-TADC IN JPT(WSS-JPT-IFLD).
       FIN-CLR-JPT-5.
           EXIT.

       CLR-JPT-10 SECTION.
       INI-CLR-JPT-10.
           MOVE ZEROES TO JPT-NUM-DIAS IN JPT(WSS-JPT-IFLD).
           MOVE ZEROES TO JPT-SGV-TAFI IN JPT(WSS-JPT-IFLD).
       FIN-CLR-JPT-10.
           EXIT.

       CLR-JPT-50 SECTION.
       INI-CLR-JPT-50.
           MOVE ZEROES TO JPT-SGV-TMIN IN JPT(WSS-JPT-IFLD).
           MOVE ZEROES TO JPT-SGV-TMAX IN JPT(WSS-JPT-IFLD).
       FIN-CLR-JPT-50.
           EXIT.
